narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Overall a great course that really brings to light how visual images have shaped US history. The discussions each week were engaging. This class is a definite recommend.

Yes!!! Like a history class on imperialism + cultural studies framework. Learned so much with regard to both. I used so many of the ideas I learned in this class for other history and humanities classes
This is a great course and definitely one that I would recommend to a student looking for a history/art history/american studies course with a lot of relevant topics and important readings.
